description:
Vanessa Bayer [Saturday Night Live, Ibiza, Barb and Star Go to Vista Del Mar ] joins Anna to talk about her favorite SNL characters, why some of the best sketches are cut for time (but you can still find them), keeping busy this last year, Make-A-Wish, finally meeting Jared Leto, formative TV shows, her freaky college roommate and more. Later in the episode, Anna and April offer some unqualified (and qualified) advice to a listener on the topic of marriage traditions and how to change them.

Learn more about April Beyer and LEVEL by visiting  www.levelconnections.com
